Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that every person has​ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that every heart holds​ ♪
