Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hidden inside every person​ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hidden inside every heart ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending absolute darkness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our ultimate spirit force ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Through charitable acts​ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Through practice of Samadhi ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And focused study ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can open this realm ♪
