Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:07.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 1\NLevitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Spirit of Truth is the guru Asahara Shoko.​
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader found salvation through early Buddhist teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In pursuit of the Supreme Truth, \NHe studied intensely to get spirit force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And earned many spiritual powers along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With their help, He became familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with the rules of cosmos, \Nwaking to keen awareness of Nature's phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this strength, \NHe strives to bring happiness to every soul.​
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In "Chouetsu Sekai", we will present key moments \Nwhen the Leader realized his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouetsu Sekai Episode 1: Levitation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This story is dedicated \Nto His struggle towards ultimate enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Reminding soaring birds, \Nhe climbs the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This air gliding phenomenon \Nis known as levitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years ago, \NI discovered it to not be a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a sublime realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:16.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,Soul of Truth\NReverend Asahara Shoko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I found myself suspended in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After the fact, \NI was enrolled in a meditation program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Something felt different...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was different.​
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite keeping my eyes closed, \NI saw odd light rays emanating from my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The top of my head felt hot.​..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How unnerving, I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't stop halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I pushed myself forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,​For an instant, I felt spiritual energy rush from the bottom of my body to the top.​
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My body started bouncing like a rubber ball.​
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,​And then, after a last leap, I found myself suspended in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced levitation for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I was focused on searching nirvana.​
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a guru, I carried on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I refined my technique through trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After levitating, I built confidence in my study methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in line with the Buddhist scriptures,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it is one of the six miracles \Nunlocked with proper training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouetsu Sekai Episode 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With none to guide him, \Nour Leader trod on an unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We hopefully conveyed fairly \NHis emotions in this episode.​
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as our Leader, those who do not study \Nunder the guidance of a guru,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,​but allow their souls to achieve nirvana \Nare known as achievers of the Supreme Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an infinitesimal amount \Nof these souls makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is all the more difficult \Nto attain without a guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But in Aum Shinrikyo, \Nour Leader succeeded in that,​
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And He is guiding us towards that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to His mastered stage, \Nour training is certain to bear fruit.​
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you also like to meet our Leader, \Nexperience spiritual awakening and develop your soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:45.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 2\NRumor from another dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the most blessed disciples,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit of Truth \NAsahara Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he know way more \Nabout ourselves than we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The hidden depths of our heart \Nare opened to our comprehension,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,much like self awareness of material bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Leader is quick to raise the flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And He bestows the most appropriate and compassionate advice on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The same may apply to whoever He meets,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,even a first-time with the Holy One \Nbares your true self in a most heartrending way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to fend for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,no attachment to cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,no need to lie to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or kowtow to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It may lay to waste before our Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll now deliver you an episode on which \Nsuch a venerable Teacher makes use of His Spirit Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy "Chouetsu Sekai" Episode 2: \NRumor from Another Dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We are 700 ordained disciples \Nand 10,000 laymen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one possibly lead so many of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the common think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But how many \Nor how far apart we all are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are irrelevant questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my Transcendental Power \Nis based on Holy Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I have the pleasure \Nto introduce you to a new mystery episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:26.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,- Aum Shinrikyo's Dojo of Supreme Truth -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Juniors train under me \Nwith the aim to become ordained monks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, they must not disregard strict rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Among them, the obligation of abstinence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding sex, it is forbidden \Nto express interest in the opposite gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, I had an astral projection shooting from my material body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it escaped to the Realm of Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In margins of the crowd, \NI overheard a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, say, have you heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiko and Yoshio have a love affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Holy One finds out, it'll go sour quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Michiko's speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop chasing after Yoshio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmh? How did I found out your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Realm of Form I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what do you find in that disciple?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him forget himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Change your mind and focus, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Guru said that no matter \Nhow many disciples you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how far apart, \Nbe aware about their frame of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the word to keep in mind is "precept."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Trainees must follow all the ten of them warily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In following order, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,About intolerance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,do not kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,About stealing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,do not steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,About Evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,do not be evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,About dishonesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,do not lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,About falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,don't speak untruthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About slandering,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,don't slander anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About duplicity,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,don't mislead one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,About attachment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,don't covet others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,About malice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,don't harm others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,About delusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,don't deny the Truth with ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we uphold these precepts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't doom ourselves \Nand reincarnate in a lower world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, why not question your daily actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,words and thoughts \Nin the light of these commandments?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:17:01.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 3\NIncarnation's Experience
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have a physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, its existence \Nimplies physical pain and tormenting thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With a body the fatality of death is around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as such, a body deteriorates over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A body also endures sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A body commands the existence of hunger and thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A body bears the discomfort of heat and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of a body \Nyou can't move as freely you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, through strict training, can't you project \Nyour conscience to an incarnation state?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The third episode of "Chouetsu Sekai" \Naddresses this topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all project towards this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An incarnation is another body that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With it, we can tread upon the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or conversely take off from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to go where you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also freely morph in appearance \Nthrough willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can teleport and traverse walls, \Nroofs, buildings and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even plunge into earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking upon water is also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, as previously said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we can get to the Realm of Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They can manifest themselves and act before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest Leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, isn't that the Guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite unusual to see Him walk alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's give Him our regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, seems like He doesn't want to interact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's odd, we can't catch up with Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even worse, He seems to outstrip us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How uncanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's return to the Dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The course starts at 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the weirded out faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw you on the streets just before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He really was meditating until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who on Earth did we spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What??
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,During a deep state of meditation, \Nyour incarnation may freely roam around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, give your very best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this, a trainee able \Nto project his incarnation is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the avatar can also end up \Nin alternate worlds and dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First hand familiarity with the inner workings \Nof the Universe and Supreme Truth starts from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is the point of using an incarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Equanimity (Upekkha) \Nseparation from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Our physical body is bound to the empirical world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because our consciousness \Nis bound to our material desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:24:02.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 4\NFateful Meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The defunct Spirit of Truth, \Nrevived through Guru Shoko Asahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was attained thanks to His study of the earliest Buddhist scriptures.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His divine power \Nstems from a source transcending human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We are always surprised \Nto see His spirit force in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The episode we deliver you this time, is a romantic foray into our leader's Transcendental Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.82,0:24:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started with "Chouetsu Sekai" part 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:11.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,- His Eminence Kalu Rinpoche -
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.90,0:25:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a life changing interaction with Kalu Rinpoche,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.94,0:25:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As if guided by the hands of fate, that Zen monk appeared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.47,0:25:30.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.06,0:26:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Zen Master, \NKalu Rinpoche, a Tibetan lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.26,0:26:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that vision I just had all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.80,0:26:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, a true Zen master \Nis still present in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.76,0:27:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I must meet him in person, no matter the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.46,0:27:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the search of that person \Nfrom my vision began.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.62,0:27:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,From Japan, with his name as only hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.18,0:27:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a plane in direction \Nof Delhi, India, Darjeeling, Calcutta.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.56,0:27:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it First landed in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.29,0:27:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to meet him right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.93,0:28:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Undoubtedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.57,0:28:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the person from my vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.54,0:28:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a head lama from the Tibetan Kagyu school.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.64,0:28:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see in this episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.71,0:28:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a deep state of meditation allows two beings \Nto meet in the Realm of Form, beyond time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.50,0:29:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Kalu Rinpoche \Nwas also able to anticipate my coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.34,0:29:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked his entourage: \N"Let me know whoever arrives today for a visit."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.29,0:29:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, both of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Were able to form \Na mutually beneficial bond around Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.10,0:30:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it mysterious to find a stranger \Nonly using a meditating vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.17,0:30:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly given how our leader and Kalu Rinpoche knew each other's existence through spirit force.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.88,0:30:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After meeting in Hong Kong,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,our Guru stayed at a temple in Darjeeling \Nwhere Kalu Rinpoche lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.88,0:30:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then, he returned the favor and preached \Nin the Mount Fuji dojo branch of Aum Shinrikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.26,0:30:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinpoche, coming from eastern Tibet, had practiced meditation in the mountains for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.95,0:30:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After China's invasion of Tibet, he found refuge \Nin Bhutan, a Buddhist country, before going to India.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.15,0:31:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, everything is subjected to impermanence...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As the hour to say good bye struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.10,0:31:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus ends episode 4 of "Chouetsu Sekai".
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.50,0:31:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.31,0:31:22.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 5\NFarewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.39,0:31:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything changes, \Ncoming to a close before vanishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.38,0:31:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lives are no exception...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful encounter \Nis always seeding a definitive farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.34,0:31:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.22,0:32:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, it applied \Nto Asahara Shoko and Kalu Rinpoche.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They also had to part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.01,0:32:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chouetsu Sekai" Episode 5: Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.40,0:32:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...This is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.95,0:32:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.25,0:32:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.30,0:32:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.78,0:32:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This was surely the voice of Kalu Rinpoche.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.62,0:33:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He thanked me, \Nand his notification made me question.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.65,0:33:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.88,0:33:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to meditate and ask the gods about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.12,0:33:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His Eminence Kalu Rinpoche... \NHis Eminence Kalu Rinpoche...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.30,0:33:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guessed so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.47,0:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kalu Rinpoche reached for me to say good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.96,0:34:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods confirmed \Nthat he is on his way to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.51,0:34:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am affirmative that he is \Neither dead or living his last moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.38,0:34:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, there is no telephone coverage \Nin the area where Rinpoche is located...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.24,0:34:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we get our visa, we'll fly to India.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.63,0:34:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.51,0:35:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A few days later, our Guru and his party \Narrived in Delhi, India, under a scorching heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.06,0:35:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving the car behind, \Nthey walked towards Rinpoche's temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.74,0:35:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.92,0:35:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How miraculous, coming so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.57,0:36:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the telegram announcing his death \Nhasn't reached its destination yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.59,0:36:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it came to my awareness through my Transcendental Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.91,0:36:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a very last contact with Rinpoche's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.40,0:36:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guru bid his last good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.91,0:36:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, he fondly remembered Rinpoche's lifetime effort to protect Buddhism during Tibet's greatest upheaval.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.67,0:37:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He never set foot on his birthplace ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.52,0:37:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In his eastern Tibet temple, a tree once planted by a young Rinpoche still stands quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.83,0:37:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for its caregiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.77,0:37:34.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 6\NThe Guru Disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.89,0:37:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago in Japan, there were people known as ninjas.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.33,0:38:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They were highly trained, especially in the field of espionage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.11,0:38:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.75,0:38:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.18,0:38:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.94,0:38:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.14,0:38:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninjas have perfected the art of stealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.40,0:38:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They disappear from the scene, as if a shape shown on a television suddenly switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.27,0:38:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But is this stunt realistically possible to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.34,0:38:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.31,0:38:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is nothing more than a myth aggrandized by popular culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.22,0:39:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Supreme Truth from the Buddhist scriptures makes it possible to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.88,0:39:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings forth a divine power beyond people's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.17,0:39:23.67,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.83,0:39:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe me closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.28,0:39:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.20,0:40:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.93,0:40:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.23,0:40:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I am not sure whether it's some optical illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.31,0:40:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a miracle, fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.35,0:40:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, fellows?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.11,0:40:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'd disappear, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.74,0:40:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, it was way too spectacular!...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.95,0:41:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An energy field enveloping my body is causing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, you should be fully aware of my spirit force,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.10,0:41:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,still, skepticism is understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.77,0:41:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A divine power beyond Humanity, the spirit force.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.41,0:41:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Guru faced many hardships in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.43,0:41:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Since His heart secedes from earthly suffering, \NHis strength opens a higher sphere of existence to Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.05,0:42:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that this mysterious power \Nspontaneously manifests.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.09,0:42:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This transcendental state
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.42,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,proves that we reached absolute Freedom, absolute Blessedness, absolute Bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.17,0:42:27.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 7\NExceeding modern medicine with spirit force!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.20,0:43:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Any adept of Aum Shinrikyo can apply to get \Na secret yoga course, directly carried out by our guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.91,0:43:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of us can recover from illnesses \Nthrough this secret yoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.91,0:43:22.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,- Aum Shinrikyo's Suginami Dojo -
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.79,0:43:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On this day as well, the leader was consulted about a certain disciple's ailment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.10,0:43:25.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.53,0:43:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamada, your cancer will recede.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.85,0:43:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay confident, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.94,0:43:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.05,0:43:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By the grace of your personal strength and practice, you will be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.85,0:43:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you \Nto Aum Shinrikyo's practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.56,0:43:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a brilliant physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.59,0:43:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please confide in his guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.68,0:44:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Vajratissa, can you also see the shadow \Non Mr. Yamada's right lung?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.81,0:44:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything bad in this spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.88,0:44:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there is nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.45,0:44:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it divine will?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.18,0:44:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You may want to check it more closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.21,0:44:45.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,- Aum Shinrikyo's Affiliated School Clinic -
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.09,0:44:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the guru really find anything through cursory inspection?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.14,0:45:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.27,0:45:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, show the image again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.65,0:45:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.60,0:45:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lymphadenitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.16,0:45:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is certainly so...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.40,0:45:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's tiny, the guru was able \Nto detect it at a very early stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.50,0:45:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, the leader knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.76,0:45:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am awestruck \Nat how His Transcendental Power preempted science.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.48,0:45:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see His power avert something so terrible, \NI feel so proud being His disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.72,0:46:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamada, the Guru said you will recover, \Nyou are in the clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.21,0:46:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.40,0:46:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.76,0:46:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I'll overcome cancer, if I place faith in our Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.90,0:46:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.73,0:46:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guru accurately pinpoints diseases through His spirit force,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.18,0:46:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and gives proper guidance towards remission.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.35,0:46:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.92,0:46:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being by the Holy One's side \Nwill make you recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.34,0:46:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The empowerment to fight against cancer \Nis an instance among these miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,While doctors unrelated to Aum Shinrikyo may fail families of patients with serious condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.39,0:47:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aum Shinrikyo helps them fight with a better chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.07,0:47:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aum Shinrikyo makes them \Nstep towards existential truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.07,0:47:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy one's Transcendental Power is really something to reckon with!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.99,0:47:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here ends "Chouetsu Sekai", \Nstay tuned for the next installment...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.49,0:47:32.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 8\NThe Far away Tibet!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.75,0:47:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's travel to Tibet, this secluded country.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.80,0:47:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Its biggest city is the 1300 years old Lhasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.34,0:47:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It has flourished as the political, economic, cultural and religious heart of Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.24,0:48:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Spirit of Truth, the noblest leader Asahara Shoko, visited this place in the summer of 1991.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.05,0:48:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be difficult for the Dalai Lama to leave India and return to Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.29,0:48:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibetan Buddhism is dying out...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.92,0:48:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.79,0:48:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I am going \Nto Drepung monastery tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.27,0:48:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Drepung monastery?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.98,0:49:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to Drepung?...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.95,0:49:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, why not also visit the First Palace, they're neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.85,0:49:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot, they're not at the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.95,0:49:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The guidebook tells:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.20,0:49:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The First Palace is westward of Drepung monastery, \N10 minutes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.53,0:49:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the same place, you'll find out once there!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.16,0:49:35.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,And on the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.74,0:49:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarer oxygen in high altitude sure is painful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.31,0:49:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I already passed out because of it, yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.69,0:50:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I now have a portable oxygen bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.07,0:50:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Guru, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.86,0:50:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you pose for the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.48,0:50:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, venerable monk, what is this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.84,0:50:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The First Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.52,0:51:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, the First Palace, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.61,0:51:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Drepung Monastery?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.66,0:51:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.37,0:51:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's what I told you, in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.49,0:51:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In my fifth life, I reincarnated as the Dalai Lama in Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.67,0:51:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember \Nthe pain of your predestination?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.28,0:51:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,About this, I remember it vividly,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.34,0:51:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my guidebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.94,0:51:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.11,0:52:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this, spirit force allows one to recall past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.62,0:52:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is called "retrocognition".
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.26,0:52:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate stage in meditation...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.41,0:52:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After passing The four levels of Samadhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.59,0:52:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Incarnation's Experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.56,0:52:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine Hearing Experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.78,0:52:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind Reading Experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.20,0:52:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth one is Transcendental Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.76,0:52:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can reach this heightened state,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.72,0:52:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you will remember what went on through cyclic metempsychosis...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.18,0:52:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of world you were born in, \Nwhat kind of life you lived, and how you died...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.12,0:53:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Past conditions, relationships long past era, \Nyour previous lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.15,0:53:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the laws of karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.64,0:53:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You will find yourself aware of so many things firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.50,0:53:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They are linked to predestination pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.93,0:53:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as accounted in our Guru's experiences \Nand secret techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.63,0:53:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Part 2 of the Secret of Transandence series is detailing everything you need to know about the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.57,0:53:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read it by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.06,0:53:43.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 9\NThe guru looks out!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.36,0:53:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Spirit of Truth, Asahara Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.95,0:54:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Closely looks after his disciples, making it difficult to devote Himself to His strenuous training.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.10,0:54:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In His infinite compassion, \NHe redeems His adepts through spirit force,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.10,0:54:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This episode is dedicated to his struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.98,0:54:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now on with "Chouetsu Sekai" \NEpisode 9: The guru looks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.36,0:54:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader Asahara Shoko was undergoing \Na demanding practice in the Genkan of his pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.66,0:55:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.78,0:55:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was standing by in a separate building \Nwith somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.58,0:55:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The guru was meant to contact us by radio, \Nprovided that he had any need.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.71,0:55:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem was that my co-disciple was bedridden with a high fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.03,0:55:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The snow keeps falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.10,0:56:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look at your temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.88,0:56:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it's this high?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.32,0:56:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Don't exert yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.81,0:56:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.91,0:56:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,, In your state? You cannot walk, stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.12,0:56:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to her, don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.51,0:56:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing outside, don't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.29,0:56:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.26,0:57:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.61,0:57:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Guru...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.04,0:58:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the guru, he was convinced \Nto go back to his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.96,0:58:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even being familiar with His formidable spirit force...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.54,0:58:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is humbling to see him use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.07,0:58:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader is so concerned about our sake, \NI nearly swoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.34,0:58:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you also like to feel as welcomed as us?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.21,0:59:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy One's Divine Spirit Force\NPart. 10\NThe Miracle Surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.86,0:59:10.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,I am Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.26,0:59:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kansai, I follow the way of the Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.91,0:59:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This last autumn, I was taken to India for more advanced education.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.33,0:59:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cried and cried so much \Nwhile taking the plane, what was the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.62,1:00:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Noriko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.27,1:00:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't properly sit, your neck will hurt again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.88,1:00:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.61,1:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.11,1:00:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your neck still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.06,1:00:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's painful!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.78,1:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling any worse than before?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.87,1:00:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.27,1:00:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Me is not fine...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.79,1:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm, how worrisome...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.36,1:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.47,1:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Noriko sweetie, wait for me, \NI'll ask the guru for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.75,1:00:52.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ω Holy Spirit of Supreme Truth Ω\N~ The noblest and purest leader Shoko Asahara ~
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.02,1:01:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, guru?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.58,1:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what's the big matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.11,1:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Noriko is crying because of neck pain, \Nstanding in a strange way, not wanting to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.92,1:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.82,1:01:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, bring Noriko here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.76,1:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Achari, leave your seat to Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.09,1:01:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.44,1:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Noriko, sit right where Achari was.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.63,1:01:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take away your pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.82,1:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.30,1:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll perform astral surgery on your pained neck...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.60,1:02:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Noriko, let's get started with Astral surgery.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.32,1:02:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.79,1:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Noriko, the astral surgery is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.81,1:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your neck won't pain you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.05,1:03:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.35,1:03:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't hurt, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.72,1:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Guru!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.87,1:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.37,1:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to kill pain with only astral surgery, \Nour Leader is out of this world!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.73,1:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit force of our guru is such,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.14,1:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma Parvati Herself would be surprised by His Shakti.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.31,1:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is like an inexhaustible spring.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.50,1:04:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there are so many people in pain, \Nplagued by intractable diseases...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guru is selflessly dispensing his mystical energy to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.25,1:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles are bound to happen with Him around.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.59,1:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, he made an elderly person unable to walk without a cane for 10 years, move around without aid.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.08,1:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Any abdominal pain making anyone wince in pain \Nis gone in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.55,1:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancer patients even get respite.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.68,1:05:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many doctors in the ranks of Aum Shinrikyo.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.23,1:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnesses to our guru's powers, \Nwhich exceed the boundaries of modern medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.08,1:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, during the healing process, \Nthe guru also takes away everyone's karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.55,1:05:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, His good deeds made Him never fall sick, \Nnot even once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.21,1:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even He was told He had two more months to live because of liver cancer caused by others karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.93,1:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason, our guru replenishes Himself through intense training.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.31,1:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He carries much of the burden by Himself,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.18,1:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so that person determined enough \Ncan reincarnate in a higher world.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.68,1:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And stay happy in this world in spite of their nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.88,1:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To strive and turn suffering into bliss, \Nalso making somebody else's suffering theirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.30,1:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the calling of the Holy One, \Nthe world's savior of souls.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.30,1:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought to you by the Sorcery Party\Nѫ~ѫ\N"Lux in Tenebris"
